        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This snare uses tightly wound springs, clockwork, and shrapnel to cause devastating damage. When a creature enters the snare's square, the trap releases, dealing 12d6 piercing damage in a deafening explosion. Everyone in a 10-foot radius of the snare's square must attempt a DC 31 Reflex save.",
